cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.SI

This paper deals with text documents and their visualization using dimensionality reduction techniques. The use of linguistic resources and corpus statistics suggests that this paper could belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). However, since the focus is on text data, cs.CL is the most likely sub-category.
